## Root Cause (Fixed)
- Next.js 14.2.35 standalone build excludes dynamic [param] routes without explicit 'dynamic' export
- Route existed in code but was excluded from build → HTTP 404 at runtime
- Solution: Add Route Segment Config before function exports

